longBusinessSummary: Cura Technologies Limited provides enterprise class software applications for organizations to manage risk, compliance, and audit framework through an automated process worldwide. It offers consultancy and technical, manpower, end to end IT solutions to energy sector. CURA Technologies Limited was formerly known as Softpro Systems Ltd and changed its name to CURA Technologies Limited in October 2010. The company was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Hyderabad, India. As of February 13, 2025, Cura Technologies Limited operates as a subsidiary of KBR Holdings Private Limited.
